So all this is telling us,

00:00:08.604 --> 00:00:09.437
with x is equal to three,

00:00:09.437 --> 00:00:12.362
the value of the function
is six, f of three is six,

00:00:12.362 --> 00:00:13.449
you could view it that way.

00:00:13.449 --> 00:00:16.963
h of three is zero, f
prime of three is six,

00:00:16.963 --> 00:00:19.313
