to three is equal to six.

00:02:08.099 --> 00:02:11.414
So this right over here is six.

00:02:11.414 --> 00:02:14.368
h of three, they give us that, too.

00:02:14.368 --> 00:02:17.782
h of three, when x is
three, the value of our

00:02:17.782 --> 00:02:19.997
function is zero.

00:02:19.997 --> 00:02:21.903
So this is zero.

00:02:21.903 --> 00:02:24.451
So this first term is you
just get six times zero,

00:02:24.451 --> 00:02:26.918
which is gonna be zero,
but we'll get to that.

